task.summary: Create basic data structure to save matrix dataset. Create dataset loader to load data from file.
Implemented linear regression with stochastic gradient.

1. Implemented zero mean unit variance normalization. 2. Finished Linear Regression on boston housing dataset (test mse: 21) 3. Implemented validation to calculate MSE. 4. Added some handy method to set and get value in matrix.
